version_description: The chords prove to be more accurate and chord change guides are placed on vowel changes.
Added a few extended chords suggested by the vocal harmonies with the solo singer in mind
Slightly different chords on certain parts that sound better
This version is unique.  It features a different arrangement, that I believe, is closest to the original chords.
It's different than other versions. It includes the INTRO Lead in and CODA Lead outro.  The chords in the verses and choruses are supported by video evidence.
This is an easier version. It's also in a different key.
More easy to play than other versions.
Updated solo including chords for rythm guitar in the solo as well as in pre chorus and outro.

song_name: To Know Her Is To Love Her
